      "span_text": "X-ray diffraction data, collected at 100K on beam line PROXIMA-1 (SOLEIL synchrotron, France) with a Dectris Pilatus 6M detector and oscillation angles of 0.2°per frame, were processed using the interactive iMOSFLM package at 3.35 Å resolution"
